markdown <<MARKDOWN
# Meet the Painter 


#### In the Neighborhood IDE, the object you will work with is from **The Painter** class. 

#### Remember, objects have attributes and methods. 

- #### An **attribute** is a characteristic the object has.
- #### A **method** is an action that an object can perform.

## The Painter Object

<div style="display: flex; width: 80%; margin: auto; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
        <div>
            <img src="https://images.code.org/98110267b6c3ee2f93700b03b95d940b-image-1741026340788.png" alt="The painter" style="width: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 10px;">
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; gap: 20px;">
            <div style="background-color: #DECEEA; color: #000000; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); text-align: center; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 200px;">
                <p style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Attributes</p>
                <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">x_location = 0</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">y_location = 0</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">direction = "east"</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">paint = 0</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div style="background-color: #DECEEA; color: #000000; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); text-align: center; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 200px;">
                <p style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">Methods</p>
                <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">move()</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">turn_left()</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5;">paint(color)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
